<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About - My Blogs</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles/layout.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles/content.css">
</head>

<body
  style="background-image: url(/Images/pexels-pixabay-262508.jpg); background-repeat: none; background-size: cover;  ">
  <%- include('partials/header.ejs') %>
    <div class="about-container">
      <header>
        <h1>Welcome to My Blogs!</h1>
        <p>This is a platform where you can read and share interesting blog posts. Our goal is to provide a space for
          passionate writers to express their thoughts and connect with readers worldwide. Feel free to browse through
          our
          blog posts and stay tuned for more exciting content.</p>
      </header>

      <section id="vision">
        <h2>Our Vision</h2>
        <p>We believe in the power of storytelling and the beauty of shared experiences. My Blogs is a community where
          writers can showcase their creativity, and readers can discover diverse perspectives from all walks of life.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section id="offer">
        <h2>What We Offer</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>A <strong>dynamic collection of blog posts</strong> spanning a variety of topics, including travel,
            technology, lifestyle, self-improvement, and more.</li>
          <li><strong>Opportunities for writers</strong> to share their voice with a global audience.</li>
          <li>A platform that encourages <strong>meaningful interactions</strong> between writers and readers.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section id="why-choose-us">
        <h2>Why Choose My Blogs?</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>User-Friendly Interface</strong>: Navigate seamlessly and discover content that resonates with
            you.
          </li>
          <li><strong>Creative Freedom</strong>: Writers can freely express their thoughts without restrictions.</li>
          <li><strong>Diverse Community</strong>: Engage with a global audience and enjoy content from various cultures
            and perspectives.</li>
          <li><strong>Continuous Improvements</strong>: We're committed to evolving and enhancing your experience.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section id="get-involved">
        <h2>Get Involved</h2>
        <p>Are you passionate about writing? Join us today! Share your unique stories, insights, and experiences.</p>
        <p>Not a writer? No problem! Browse our curated blog posts, leave comments, and connect with like-minded
          individuals.</p>
      </section>
      <section id="testimonial-cards">
        <h2>Testimonials</h2>
        <div class="card-container">
          <!-- Card 1 -->
          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <img src="/Images/female-icon.jpeg" alt="Profile Picture of Anna T." class="profile-picture">
            <h3>Anna T.</h3>
            <h4>Subject: A Fantastic Platform</h4>
            <p>"My Blogs is my favorite platform for both reading and writing. It’s incredibly easy to use, and the
              community is amazing."</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Card 2 -->
          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <img src="/Images/male-icon.jpeg" alt="Profile Picture of James L." class="profile-picture">
            <h3>James L.</h3>
            <h4>Subject: Great Support for Writers</h4>
            <p>"As a writer, I’ve found a supportive and engaging audience here. I love it!"</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Card 3 -->
          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <img src="/Images/female-icon.jpeg" alt="Profile Picture of Sarah P." class="profile-picture">
            <h3>Sarah P.</h3>
            <h4>Subject: Wonderful Community</h4>
            <p>"The community on My Blogs is incredibly welcoming and interactive. I always feel inspired after reading
              posts here."</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Card 4 -->
          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <img src="/Images/male-icon.jpeg" alt="Profile Picture of Michael R." class="profile-picture">
            <h3>Michael R.</h3>
            <h4>Subject: Easy to Use</h4>
            <p>"I love how simple and intuitive the platform is. It makes reading and writing blogs so enjoyable."</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="team">
        <h2>Meet the Team</h2>
        <p>Our team is composed of passionate individuals who work tirelessly to make My Blogs a welcoming and enjoyable
          space for everyone.</p>
      </section>

      <section id="image-gallery">
        <h2>Image Gallery</h2>
        <div class="image-placeholder">
          <video src="/Images/4746616-uhd_3840_2160_30fps.mp4" muted loop autoplay
            alt="Collaborating on creative projects">
        </div>
        <div class="image-placeholder">
          <img src="/Images/pexels-andrew-3178818.jpg" alt="Diverse group of readers and writers">
        </div>
        <div class="image-placeholder">
          <img src="/Images/pexels-drew-williams-1285451-3098619.jpg"
            alt="Blog post being written on a modern interface">
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="stay-connected">
        <h2>Stay Connected</h2>
        <p>Follow us on social media to get updates on new blog posts, features, and events.</p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <%- include("partials/footer.ejs") %>
</body>

</html>